review: The service is terrible. Been there twice with my daughter. I always order her a kid's pizza: first time we waited over an hour to get her pizza after several complaints, we even had time to eat our own meal! They gave us a free drink but I had to get up several times and when I finally started talking very loud they took me seriously. For some reason, I went there again and same thing happened with the kid's pizza.  I'll never go there again. Servers barely speak english.
